{"tid":2509964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"樂富大家樂雞湯樣本葡萄球菌過量","createTime":"2021-04-29T22:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T22:21:45.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c71da959f6a09e23f07b0de57559d3f6a36b7d45","tid":2509964,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T22:21:45.000Z","msg":"食安中心在樂富一間快餐店，驗出一個雞湯樣本葡萄球菌過量。食安中心跟進一宗食物投訴時，在樂富廣場大家樂抽取一個舞茸無花果雞湯樣本化驗，發現凝固酶陽性葡萄球菌過量。中心已要求食肆暫停出售有關食品，正跟進事件。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389465&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=c311270f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389465</a>"}]}